akeasy and oauth2 modes' org metadata. Permanently unauthenticated (idp-design.md §6)."},{"name":"memberships","description":"Dev-idp memberships CRUD. Idempotent on (user_id, organization_id) for create. Permanently unauthenticated."},{"name":"users","description":"Dev-idp users CRUD. The local-mode currentUser (local-speakeasy / oauth2-1 / oauth2) references rows in this table by id (idp-design.md §3, §5). Permanently unauthenticated."}]}